The input array `rolls` must not be null.
The length of the input array `rolls` must be equal to `m`.
The value of each element in the input array `rolls` must be between 1 and 6 (inclusive).
The value of `mean` must be between 1 and 6 (inclusive).
The value of `n` must be between 1 and 10^5 (inclusive).
The sum of `n + m` must be divisible by `n + m`.
